show.description: The storyline centers on Chloe, who, after marrying a stranger to save her family, discovers that her husband is Robert Kensington, a ruthless CEO with deadly enemies. As the narrative unfolds, Chloe's awakened werewolf genes reveal her as Arthur's destined mate, adding a supernatural twist to the tale.
